Two parts in this collection, first part complete 23 first years 1948-1970, second part complete 19 years 1987-2005, all MINT no tabs. In total 1192 stamps and 46 Souvenir sheets (plus 25 from booklets and variants). Only on first years can be found some hinged stamps. It's a complete 42 years Israel stamps collection, all stamps on hingeless heavy 2 album pages, no stain all clean. Postage is extra. Each part can be sell separately, first part for 600 and second for 475.
